# Netlify redirects. Format: <from> <to> <status>
#
# Hotel slug changes. A hotel's slug is its URL segment, so when a property
# rebrands and we rename the slug, the old URL has to keep resolving — both for
# anything already indexed and for links out in the wild.

# Thompson Hollywood -> The Hollywood Grande, Autograph Collection (2025-07-29,
# Hyatt to Marriott). Renamed 2026-07-18.
